---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Groves
permalink: /groves/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<header>
  <h1>Groves</h1>
  <p class="landing-subtitle">Curated clusters of related ideas — pathways through a theme.</p>
</header>

<p>A <strong>grove</strong> is a curated cluster page that gathers related notes into a coherent pathway. It is a page type, not a maturity stage. Each grove explores a theme from multiple angles, helping you see how ideas connect.</p>

<div class="grove-cards">
  {%- for note in collections.groves -%}
    <a href="{{ note.url }}" class="grove-card">
      <span class="grove-card-icon">🪴</span>
      <span class="grove-card-title">{% if note.data.title %}{{ note.data.title }}{% else %}{{ note.fileSlug }}{% endif %}</span>
    </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
